snippet.title: Sweet Meat (Beta) -1st Trailer
snippet.description:
Sweet Meat Rush: Hell of a Runner
Play it on Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.oneeyeant.sweetmeatr
(Coming really soon to the App Store)

Sweet Meat is a game with cute characters that love to run agains lovely threats like chainsaws, minefields, kicking unicorns, storms of burned chickens, and a lot more of tender obstacles & dangers. (funny cartoonist violence). 
But the real deal is, that it has an innovative tweak: Twitter users can play God and change the gameplay of all active players in real time!!
